quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  44,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  44,1,Haa-Meeem
  44,2,is kitaab roshan ki qasam
  44,3,ke hum ne is ko mubarak raat mein nazil farmaya hum to rasta dikhaane walay hain
  44,4,isi raat mein tamam hikmat ke kaam Faisal kiye jatay hain
  44,5,( yani ) hamaray haan se hukum ho kar. be shak hum hi ( paighambar ko ) bhaijtay hain
  44,6,( yeh ) tumahray perwar-digaar ki rehmat hai. woh to suneney wala jan-nay wala hai
  44,7,asmano aur zameen ka aur jo kuch un dono mein hai sab ka maalik. bashart e kay tum log yaqeen karne walay ho
  44,8,is ke siwa koi mabood nahi. ( wohi ) jalataa hai aur ( wohi ) maarta hai. wohi tumhara aur tumahray baap dada ka perwar-digaar hai
  44,9,lekin yeh log shak mein khail rahay hain
  44,10,to is din ka intzaar karo ke aasman se Sarih dhuwan niklay ga
  44,11,jo logon par chhaa jaye ga. yeh dard dainay wala azaab hai
  44,12,ae perwar-digaar hum se is azaab ko daur kar hum imaan laatay hain
  44,13,( is waqt ) un ko nasiyaat kahan mufeed hogi jab ke un ke paas paighambar aachukay jo khol khol kar bayan kar dete hain
  44,14,phir unhon ne un se munh phair liya aur kehnay lagey ( yeh to ) parhaya howa ( aur ) deewana hai
  44,15,hum to thoray dinon azaab taall dete hain ( magar ) tum phir kufar karne lagtay ho
  44,16,jis din hum barri sakht pakar pakren ge to be shak intiqam le kar choden ge
  44,17,aur un se pehlay hum ne qoum firaon ki azmaish ki aur un ke paas aik aalii qader paighambar aeye
  44,18,( jinhon ne ) yeh ( kaha ) ke khuda ke bundon ( yani bani Israel ) ko mere hawalay kardo mein tumhara amanat daar paighambar hon
  44,19,aur khuda ke samnay sar kashi nah karo. mein tumahray paas khuli Daleel le kar aaya hon
  44,20,aur is ( baat ) se ke tum mujhe sangsar karo apne aur tumahray perwar-digaar ki panah mangta hon
  44,21,aur agar tum mujh par imaan nahi laatay to mujh se allag ho jao
  44,22,tab moose ne apne perwar-digaar se dua ki ke yeh nafarman log hain
  44,23,( khuda ne farmaya ke ) mere bundon ko raton raat le kar chalay jao aur ( fravni ) zaroor tumhara taqub karen ge
  44,24,aur darya se ( ke ) khushk ( ho raha hoga ) paar ho jao ( tumahray baad ) un ka tamam lashkar duubo diya jaye ga
  44,25,woh log bohat se baagh aur chashmay chore gay
  44,26,aur khityan aur nafees makaan
  44,27,aur aaraam ki cheeze jin mein aishkiya karte they
  44,28,isi terhan ( howa ) aur hum ne dosray logon ko un cheezon ka maalik bana diya
  44,29,phir un par nah to aasman ko aur zameen ko rona aaya aur nah un ko mohlat hi di gayi
  44,30,aur hum ne bani Israel ko zillat ke azaab se nijaat di
  44,31,( yani ) firaon se. be shak woh sarkash ( aur ) hadd se nikla howa tha
  44,32,aur hum ne bani Israel ko ahal aalam se danista munhtakhibkiya tha
  44,33,aur un ko aisi nishanain di theen jin mein Sarih azmaish thi
  44,34,yeh log yeh kehte hain
  44,35,ke hamein sirf pehli dafaa ( yani aik baar ) marna hai aur ( phir ) uthna nahi
  44,36,pas agar tum sachey ho to hamaray baap dada ko ( zindah kar ) lao
  44,37,bhala yeh achay hain ya tba ki qoum aur woh log jo tum se pehlay ho chukay hain. hum ne un ( sab ) ko halaak kardiya. be shak woh gunehgaar they
  44,38,aur hum ne asmano aur zameen ko aur jo kuch un mein hai un ko khailtay hue nahi banaya
  44,39,un ko hum ne tadbeer se pedakiya hai lekin aksar log nahi jantay
  44,40,kuch shak nahi ke faislay ka din un sab ( ke utney ) ka waqt hai
  44,41,jis din koi dost kisi dost ke kuch kaam nah aeye ga aur nah un ko madad miley gi
  44,42,magar jis par khuda meharbani kere. woh to ghalib aur meharban hai
  44,43,bilashuba تھوہر ka darakht
  44,44,gunehgaar ka khana hai
  44,45,jaisay pighla howa tanba. piton mein ( is terhan ) khole ga
  44,46,jis terhan garam pani kholta hai
  44,47,( hukum diya jaye ga ke ) is ko pakar lau aur khinchte hue dozakh ke bichon beech le jao
  44,48,phir is ke sir par kholta howa pani undail do ( ke azaab par ) azaab ( ho )
  44,49,( ab ) maza chakh. to barri izzat wala ( aur ) sardar hai
  44,50,yeh wohi ( dozakh ) hai jis mein tum log shakkiya karte they
  44,51,be shak parhaizgaar log aman ke maqam mein hon ge
  44,52,( yani ) baghoon aur chashmo mein
  44,53,Hareer ka bareek aur dabeez libaas pehan kar aik dosray ke samnay baithy hon ge
  44,54,is terhan ( ka haal hoga ) aur hum barri barri aankhon wali safaid rang ki aurton se un ke jore lagayen ge
  44,55,wahan khatir jama se har qisam ke meway mngwayin ge ( aur khayen ge )
  44,56,( aur ) pehli dafaa ke marnay ke siwa ( ke mrchke they ) mout ka maza nahi chakhain ge. aur khuda un ko dozakh ke azaab se bacha le ga
  44,57,yeh tumahray perwar-digaar ka fazl hai. yahi to barri kamyabi hai
  44,58,hum ne is ( quran ) ko tumhari zabaan mein aasaan kardiya hai taakay yeh log nasiyaat pakren
  44,59,pas tum bhi intzaar karo yeh bhi intzaar kar rahay hain
